  What WebGL command will retrieve values from a *color buffer*?

  - :code:`gl.readPixels()`

    + Correct.

  - :code:`gl.readColorBuffer()`

    - Incorrect. There is no such function.

  - :code:`gl.getPixelColor()`

    - Incorrect. There is no such function.

  - :code:`gl.atPixel()`

    - Incorrect. There is no such function.